                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1792" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0342</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8778 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京同仁堂（成都）健康酒有限公司战略调整？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Beijing Tongrentang Health Wine (chengdu) co., LTD., Strategic Adjustment？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">敬永春</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京同仁堂（成都）健康酒有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略调整；行业竞争；宏观环境；资源与能力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">strategic adjustment; industrial competition; macro-environment; resource &amp;amp; capability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京同仁堂（成都）健康酒有限公司是中国北京同仁堂（集团）有限公司旗下北京同仁堂（四川）健康药业有限公司的全资子公司，公司主要从事高端配制型白酒的生产和销售活动。2010年其配制型白酒系列产品上市后，取得了良好的销售业绩。但随着宏观环境和行业环境发生根本性变化，公司的发展遇到了较大困难，需要进行适当战略调整以解决公司未来应该如何发展的问题。本案例通过介绍公司内部的资源与能力状况、公司所处行业环境和宏观环境关键战略因素发生的变化以及公司遇到的多重两难选择，为学员学习和应用战略管理相关知识（PEST、五力模型、EFE、IFE、VRIO、SWOT等）提供了典型的分析讨论素材。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Beijing tongrentang health wine (chengdu) co., LTD(TRT-CD), A subsidiary of the Beijing tongrentang (group) co., LTD（TRT-BJ）, once mainly engaged in high-end integrated alcoholic beverages production and sales. The first serious of products entered the market in 2010, in the next few years it made fairly good achievements. But when the macro-environments and the industrial environments changed greatly at the beginning of 2013, TRT-CD found it is so hard to run the firm just as well as before. So, “what are the real reasons caused the difficulties? How to resolve them? What should we do? Where should we go?” gradually became into the urgent problems before the board of directors. In this case, the characteristics of the firm are introduced firstly. Secondly we stated changes of environment, especially the change of key strategic factors. And then we ask the students to do some analyses and discussions to match the factors from internal and outer environment to draw some conclusions about the adjustments of the strategy of the firm. this case provided typical materials and is benefit for students to learn and use some basic strategic analysis tools, for example, PEST、 five forces model、EFE、IFE、SWOT and so on.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业战略制定</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-11</td>
                            </tr>
